Speech to Text — release signing key(s)
=======================================

This file will contain the ASCII-armored GPG public key used to sign release
checksum manifests (`SHA256SUMS.asc`). Import it with:

    gpg --import KEYS

and verify a download with `scripts/verify-release.sh`.

The key block and its fingerprint are added here when the first signed release
(1.3.0) is cut. Until then, this file is a placeholder.

